cross: Paphiopedilum Red Shift x Paphiopedilum charlesworthii
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: One extremely dark flower on one 21-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal large, rounded, and oblong, slightly reflexed, dark burgundy; synsepal ovate acuminate, translucent burgundy; petals broadly lanceolate, ciliate at margin, dark burgundy; pouch intense burgundy; staminode white suffused burgundy, small green central node; substance firm; texture glossy.
